            <thetext>As with bug 7081, there is a upcoming demand for a drawer widget.

http://bugzilla.qooxdoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=7081

to display the MasterPage inside a Popup widget, look weird, when user uses a toolbar or something similar inside the popup.

The popup widget looks to complex and it looks only good, if a List is contained inside. 

That is why we need a drawer widget for being able to display a page as an overlay before another detail page.

An animation for slide in/out can be very easily realized.  The drawer should be anchored in one of four directions: &quot;left&quot;,&quot;right&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;top&quot;. According to this orientation, two properties are relevant: &quot;width&quot;,&quot;height&quot;.

This drawer should used by MasterDetail container for solving bug 7081.</thetext>
